#: ../../chapters/djing_with_mixxx.rst:341
msgid ""
"Now that you have loaded tracks into the Auto DJ playlist, you can activate "
"Auto DJ as follows:"
msgstr "Ora che hai caricato brani nella playlist Auto DJ, puoi attivare Auto DJ come segue:"

#: ../../chapters/djing_with_mixxx.rst:344
msgid ""
"Click on the *Auto DJ* icon in the sidebar to switch to the :guilabel:`Auto "
"DJ` view of the library."
msgstr "Fare clic sull'icona *Auto DJ* nella barra laterale per passare alla vista :guilabel:`Auto DJ` della libreria."

#: ../../chapters/djing_with_mixxx.rst:346
msgid "Click the :guilabel:`Enable Auto DJ` button."
msgstr "Fai clic sul pulsante :guilabel:`Attiva Auto DJ`."

#: ../../chapters/djing_with_mixxx.rst:347
msgid ""
"The first tracks from your list are loaded into the decks and the playback "
"starts."
msgstr "Le prime tracce della tua lista vengono caricate nei deck e la riproduzione inizia."

#: ../../chapters/djing_with_mixxx.rst:349
msgid ""
"Mixxx will continue to automatically mix until the Auto DJ playlist is "
"empty."
msgstr "Mixxx continuerà a mixare automaticamente fino a quando la playlist Auto DJ è vuota."

#: ../../chapters/djing_with_mixxx.rst:350
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Disable Auto DJ` button to stop the automatic mixing"
msgstr "Fare clic sul pulsante :guilabel:`Disabilita Auto DJ` per interrompere il missaggio automatico"

#: ../../chapters/djing_with_mixxx.rst:352
msgid ""
"You can add a track to the end of the Auto DJ playlist once it is played "
"instead of removing it. Set :menuselection:`Preferences --> Auto DJ --> Re-"
"queue tracks after playback --> On`."
msgstr ""
